  ('social-worker-moex-06480', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-103-7c9828ae', 'sub-social-worker-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '社會工作專業強調的六大核心價值觀當中，其一為稱職（competence），由此一價值觀所衍申之主要倫理 原則為何？', '["客觀性", "講求績效責任", "個別化", "非論斷之心態"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:34+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a3d845e75c7c", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ca9f253103ce", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "103100", "c": "110", "s": "0601", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作", "year": "103", "exam_name": "103年第二次專技醫師中醫師分階段、中醫師營養師心理師護理師社會工作師、法醫師語言聽力牙體技術師考試", "original_question_number": 27, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-06481', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-103-7c9828ae', 'sub-social-worker-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '雖然在社會工作實務中，工作者可能會視狀況運用行為學派之理論架構，但行為學派或行為主義在社會 工作實務上會面臨一些限制，下列何種特性屬於此一學派之限制？', '["不適用在短期個案", "互動性影響而非線性影響", "難用於極為複雜的個案", "可使用在處理貧窮問題"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:34+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a3d845e75c7c", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ca9f253103ce", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "103100", "c": "110", "s": "0601", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作", "year": "103", "exam_name": "103年第二次專技醫師中醫師分階段、中醫師營養師心理師護理師社會工作師、法醫師語言聽力牙體技術師考試", "original_question_number": 28, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
